business_rules_view_code:
create or replace view business_rules.xmlmetric_s_xmlinterface as
select 
    bo."business key for hub xmlmetric",    -- business key for business layer
    bo.ldts,                              -- load time satellite xmlmetric > xmlinterface > default of vi_xml_metric_u_staging
    bo.updated,                           -- updated from satellite xmlmetric > xmlinterface > default of vi_xml_metric_u_staging
    bo.component_name,                    -- component_name from satellite xmlmetric > xmlinterface > default of vi_xml_metric_u_staging
    bo.component_version,                 -- component_version from satellite xmlmetric > xmlinterface > default of vi_xml_metric_u_staging
    bo.specmetric_name,                   -- specmetric_name from satellite xmlmetric > xmlinterface > default of vi_xml_metric_u_staging
    bo.metric_name,                       -- metric_name from satellite xmlmetric > xmlinterface > default of vi_xml_metric_u_staging
    bo.metric_value                       -- metric_value from satellite xmlmetric > xmlinterface > default of vi_xml_metric_u_staging

  from businessobjects.xmlmetric_s_xmlinterface bo
;
